<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Restaurant</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* Custom CSS for additional styling */
        body {
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        .heading {
            color: #e53e3e;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .text-description {
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
        }
        .image-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .image-container img {
            width: 45%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .image-container img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #e53e3e;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            background-color: #c53030;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="image-container mb-4">
            <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/halal-food-serve-table_53876-71224.jpg" alt="Image 1">
            <img src="https://img.freepik.com/free-photo/fettuccine-with-tomato-sauce-minced-meat-garnished-with-grated-parmesan_141793-1778.jpg" alt="Image 2">
        </div>
        <h1 class="heading mb-4">About Our Restaurant</h1>
        <p class="text-description">Welcome to our restaurant! We pride ourselves on offering delicious meals made with the freshest ingredients sourced locally whenever possible.</p>
        <p class="text-description">Our chefs are passionate about creating culinary delights that will tantalize your taste buds and keep you coming back for more.</p>
        <p class="text-description">Whether you're joining us for a casual meal with friends or a special occasion, our friendly staff is here to ensure you have an unforgettable dining experience.</p>
        <p class="text-description">We also offer catering services for events of all sizes. Contact us to learn more about how we can make your next event extra special!</p>
        <p class="text-description">Thank you for choosing our restaurant. We look forward to serving you soon!</p>
        <button class="cta-button mt-6">Contact Us for Reservations</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
